author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Mexico Reports 132 New Coronavirus Cases as Totals Reach 717
description: Mexican health officials announced 132 new cases of the novel coronavirus (COVID-19) on Friday as the new totals reach 717 confirmed cases and 12 fatalities. Five medical care providers also became infected while treating patients of the pandemic.
